( 
  select concept_id from @vocabulary_database_schema.CONCEPT where concept_id in (4142479)
UNION  select c.concept_id
  from @vocabulary_database_schema.CONCEPT c
  join @vocabulary_database_schema.CONCEPT_ANCESTOR ca on c.concept_id = ca.descendant_concept_id
  and ca.ancestor_concept_id in (4142479)
  and c.invalid_reason is null

) I
) C

SELECT 11 as codeset_id, c.concept_id FROM (select distinct I.concept_id FROM
( 
  select concept_id from @vocabulary_database_schema.CONCEPT where concept_id in (320741,4096099,44782752,44811347,45757409,4203836,4205652,4124856,4203618,4318407,762047,44782762,435565,45757410,4033521,762049,4055089,440738,444247,40481089,193512,45773536,36712892,4234997,439838,4133004,44782759,444097,4327889,4149782,762048,4317289)
UNION  select c.concept_id
  from @vocabulary_database_schema.CONCEPT c
  join @vocabulary_database_schema.CONCEPT_ANCESTOR ca on c.concept_id = ca.descendant_concept_id
  and ca.ancestor_concept_id in (44782752,40481089,4133004)
  and c.invalid_reason is null

) I
LEFT JOIN
(
  select concept_id from @vocabulary_database_schema.CONCEPT where concept_id in (36712971,435887,438820,4179911,4089917)
UNION  select c.concept_id
  from @vocabulary_database_schema.CONCEPT c
  join @vocabulary_database_schema.CONCEPT_ANCESTOR ca on c.concept_id = ca.descendant_concept_id
  and ca.ancestor_concept_id in (36712971,435887,438820,4089917)
  and c.invalid_reason is null

) E ON I.concept_id = E.concept_id
WHERE E.concept_id is null
) C

concept_set_sql:
SELECT 16 as codeset_id, c.concept_id FROM (select distinct I.concept_id FROM
( 
  select concept_id from @vocabulary_database_schema.CONCEPT where concept_id in (2788719,42898019,2788725,2789177,2785952,2788715,2788973,2788979,4182536,2788711,2788716,2788734,2788717,2788713,42898020)
UNION  select c.concept_id
  from @vocabulary_database_schema.CONCEPT c
  join @vocabulary_database_schema.CONCEPT_ANCESTOR ca on c.concept_id = ca.descendant_concept_id
  and ca.ancestor_concept_id in (2788719,42898019,2788725,2789177,2785952,2788715,2788973,2788979,4182536,2788711,2788716,2788734,2788717,2788713,42898020)
  and c.invalid_reason is null

) I
) C

SELECT 29 as codeset_id, c.concept_id FROM (select distinct I.concept_id FROM
( 
  select concept_id from @vocabulary_database_schema.CONCEPT where concept_id in (4295287)
UNION  select c.concept_id
  from @vocabulary_database_schema.CONCEPT c
  join @vocabulary_database_schema.CONCEPT_ANCESTOR ca on c.concept_id = ca.descendant_concept_id
  and ca.ancestor_concept_id in (4295287)
  and c.invalid_reason is null

) I
) C

( 
  select concept_id from @vocabulary_database_schema.CONCEPT where concept_id in (432923,376713,4148906,4108952,4111708)
UNION  select c.concept_id
  from @vocabulary_database_schema.CONCEPT c
  join @vocabulary_database_schema.CONCEPT_ANCESTOR ca on c.concept_id = ca.descendant_concept_id
  and ca.ancestor_concept_id in (376713,4148906,4108952,4111708)
  and c.invalid_reason is null

) I
LEFT JOIN
(
  select concept_id from @vocabulary_database_schema.CONCEPT where concept_id in (4345688,42872427,4249574)
UNION  select c.concept_id
  from @vocabulary_database_schema.CONCEPT c
  join @vocabulary_database_schema.CONCEPT_ANCESTOR ca on c.concept_id = ca.descendant_concept_id
  and ca.ancestor_concept_id in (4345688,42872427)
  and c.invalid_reason is null

) E ON I.concept_id = E.concept_id
WHERE E.concept_id is null
) C
